data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY, OCTOBER 7, 11 AM - 2 PM  Back on market - no fault of seller/home.  Pride of ownership shines throughout this home. Quiet neighborhood across from greenbelt. Open floor plan with stainless kitchen appliances, granite counters and pantry. Flexible space could be living room, den or formal dining room. Family, Dining and Kitchen flow beautifully with gas fireplace and sliding doors to covered patio. Fully fenced low maintenance yard. Bedrooms are good sized and double door entry to Primary Suite with walk in closet and bath.  Fully fenced lovely back yard.  Home is located at end of subdivision across from wetlands - no neighbors across the street!  Very quiet and beautiful.  2.5% assumable VA loan available to qualified veterans.
